WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:05.121
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:06.456 --> 00:07.957
Hey, fellas, do me a favor.

00:07.957 --> 00:09.459
You guys have had a few drinks.

00:09.459 --> 00:11.461
Sit down. Let me buy you some coffee.

00:11.461 --> 00:12.462
Aw, th-thanks anyway, Sam,

00:12.462 --> 00:14.214
but everything's under control.

00:14.214 --> 00:16.049
Pete hasn't had a thing
to drink all night.

00:16.549 --> 00:17.550
He's our designated driver.

00:17.550 --> 00:20.053
Oh, I'm glad to hear it.
That's a good idea, Pete.

00:20.053 --> 00:21.438
I'm not the designated driver.

00:21.438 --> 00:25.358
I thought you were.

00:25.358 --> 00:28.862
No, no, I-I'm not
the designated driver.

00:28.862 --> 00:30.230
What about you, Mark?

00:30.230 --> 00:32.698
I'm with Sam. I think we
ought to try it sometime.

00:34.701 --> 00:36.703
Wait right here. I'm
gonna call you a cab.

00:43.209 --> 00:44.711
Speaking of driving someone home,

00:44.711 --> 00:47.080
since you've been drinking,
I'd be happy to give you a lift.

00:47.080 --> 00:47.914
Oh, thanks, but, uh,

00:48.415 --> 00:49.916
all I've been drinking is soda water.

00:50.417 --> 00:51.418
Oh.

00:51.418 --> 00:53.803
Well, in that case, Woody,
make me a double martini.

00:56.089 --> 01:00.477
One of us is getting
driven home tonight.

